Package semsim.model.physical

Class PhysicalProcess

java.lang.Object
semsim.SemSimObject
semsim.model.SemSimComponent
semsim.model.physical.PhysicalModelComponent
semsim.model.physical.PhysicalProcess
All Implemented Interfaces:
Annotatable
Direct Known Subclasses:
CustomPhysicalProcess, ReferencePhysicalProcess
public abstract class PhysicalProcess
extends PhysicalModelComponent
Class for working with the physical processes simulated in a model. Analogous to 'OPB:Physics process': A physics processual entity that is the flow or exchange of matter, energy and/or information amongst dynamical entities that are partcipants in the process.
Author:
mneal
